{"tid":1801521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[天下烏鴉]  稱示威者破壞設施 印度政府下令230人賠巨款","createTime":"2019-12-28T16:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T07:14:15.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8341aae284eef045c61808372e2ce0d536584e5","tid":1801521,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"稱示威者破壞設施 印度政府下令230人賠巨款<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1668030/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4230%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%A0%E5%B7%A8%E6%AC%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1668030%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4230%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E6%25AC%25BE&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=d9bf83fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1668030%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4230%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E6%25AC%25BE&h=e0400e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1668030/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%A8%B1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4230%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%A0%E5%B7%A8%E6%AC%BE</a><br />\n<br />\n印度國會本月較早前通過被視為歧視穆斯林的《公民身分法》修正案，引發全國抗議浪潮。激進示威者與防暴警察爆發衝突，並破壞公共財物。印度政府採取強硬鎮壓行動，在暴力示威最嚴重的北方邦，當局向最少230名據稱在示威中破壞公共財物的人，發出索償通知書，要求他們就公共財物損失賠償巨款，威脅充公他們的私人財產來賠償。但<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有收到通知書的人聲稱自己並沒有參加示威。<br />\n<br />\n北方邦官員周四表示，他們向最少230名涉嫌在示威中破壞公共財物的人，發出索取（公共財物）賠償通知書，當中大部分是穆斯林，索償總數以千萬計盧比（約109萬港元）計。目前未清楚他們當中有多少人被控暴動罪或其他罪名，而各人均未被法庭定罪。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n北方邦爆發的反修正案暴力示威最嚴重，在全國各地示威導致21死亡中，最少有15人來自該邦。北方邦也是全國人口最多邦份，2億人口中有兩成是穆斯林，是穆斯林與印度教徒衝突的火藥庫。 <br />\n<br />\n《公民身分法》修正案，本月10日和11日相繼在印度國會下議院和上議院通過，隨後由總理莫迪簽署成為法律。它允許在2014年12月31日前，因為受到宗教逼害從阿富汗、孟加拉、巴基斯坦等國逃到印度的印度教、錫克教、佛教、耆那教、祆教（俗稱拜火教）和天主教徒取得印度公民身分，但卻排除穆斯林。批評人士指出，《公民身分法》修正案歧視穆斯林，並破壞印度的世俗憲法。<br />\n<br />\n全國數以十萬計示威者包括大學生上街示威，與警察爆發衝突，並破壞公共財物。"},{"pid":"30e5fc682af09611be2bbdcbe2c37ebc37a2757c","tid":1801521,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥) (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801519</a><br />\n<br />\n上水和你shop聽日仲有<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801500</a>"},{"pid":"ce3620643c451aae97fdfcb4aff68a7972f68ce9","tid":1801521,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你shop 升級：熱情香港 好客之道 又點少得你！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801116</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hk